[#CC4125]\"></span><p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base uppercase tracking-[0.25em] sm:tracking-[0.35em] text-[#20B2AA] __className_ebdfad\">Restaurants &amp; Nightlife</p></div><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black uppercase leading-[0.95] text-[#36454F] md:text-7xl __className_ebdfad\">Eat and<br/>Drink.</h2><div class=\"mt-4 h-[3px] w-20 sm:w-24 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#CC4125] via-[#20B2AA] to-transparent\"></div><p class=\"mt-5 sm:mt-6 text-xl sm:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-[#36454F]/60 __className_ebdfad\">Discover premium dining destinations, social venues, networking lounges, and curated culinary experiences designed around the energy of Funinfate.</p></div><div class=\"mb-5 lg:hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[24px] sm:rounded-[32px] border border-[#F5DEB3]/15 bg-[#36454F]/80 p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-sm h-full\"><div class=\"absolute -right-20 -top-20 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-[#20B2AA]/25 blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"absolute -left-16 -bottom-16 h-48 w-48 rounded-full bg-[#CC4125]/20 blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#20B2AA] __className_ebdfad\">Culinary Experiences</p><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black uppercase leading-none text-[#F5DEB3] __className_ebdfad\">Taste The<br/>Future Of<br/>Funinfate</h2><p class=\"mt-4 sm:mt-5 max-w-md text-xl sm:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-[#F5DEB3]/70 __className_ebdfad\">From immersive rooftop lounges to curated chef experiences, discover the restaurants, nightlife, and social spaces powering the energy of Funinfate.</p><div class=\"mt-5 sm:mt-6 h-px w-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#CC4125] to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"mt-5 sm:mt-6 flex flex-col xs:flex-row flex-wrap gap-3 sm:gap-4\"><a class=\"group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[#20B2AA] px-5 sm:px-6 py-2.5 sm:py-3 text-base font-semibold text-[#020817] transition hover:scale-[1.02] hover: